{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735570/extras/titre-steampunk-gravity.png?t=1667212634\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The story</h2><br>London, 1871, we are in the middle of the <strong>Steampunk</strong> era of the Victorian era.<br>A mad genius wants to destroy the city from underground to show his power and impose his will on the whole of England.<br><br>To carry out his evil plan, he has scattered explosive charges  throughout underground London, in strategic places, to be detonated soon.<br>Fortunately, we were able to find a few that our agents were able to defuse.<br><br><strong>You Are Our Last Chance!</strong><br>With your <strong>revolutionary turbine ship</strong>, you will descend into the depths of the city to retrieve our agents, as well as the explosive charges they have stored in containers.<br>Good luck!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735570/extras/titre-vaisseau-en.png?t=1667212634\" /><br><br>Your ship is a flying submarine, powered by powerful revolutionary turbines, allowing you to propel yourself both in the air and in the water.<br>You'll need practice to handle it with dexterity!<br><br>You will have to recovery men and put them on the platforms that you will use to repair your ship.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735570/extras/water-man.gif?t=1667212634\" /><br><br>You will also need to recovery heavy containers containing explosive charges and place them on the platforms.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735570/extras/water-man6.gif?t=1667212634\" /><br><br>Your ship can navigate underwater, but beware of the many devastating obstacles!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735570/extras